---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Products"
  description="Shariah-compliant financing, energy storage, and residential solutions supporting Pakistan’s transition to renewable energy."
>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-hero-content">
        <p class="page-eyebrow">Products</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Clean Energy Solutions for Every Scale</h1>
        <div class="page-subtitle-group">
          <p class="page-subtitle">
            Shariah-compliant renewable energy and storage solutions designed for commercial,
            industrial, and residential partners across Pakistan.
          </p>
          <p class="page-subtitle">
            Backed by an experienced team and proven track record, we support Pakistan’s
            transition to renewable energy with tailored financing and technology-forward
            infrastructure.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Commercial & Industrial</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Customized solutions for IPPs and C&I clients to deliver clean power, optimize
          operating costs, and support long-term energy resilience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Development and Financing of Solar/Wind Projects</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
              We develop and finance solar and wind energy plants for C&amp;I clients and IPPs,
              delivering clean power under long-term contracts that optimize efficiency and
              cost effectiveness.
            </p>
            <ul class="product-list" role="list">
              <li>Power Purchase Agreements (PPAs)</li>
              <li>Equipment Rental Agreements (ERAs)</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="definition-grid">
              <div class="card definition-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="definition-title">Power Purchase Agreement (PPA)</p>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    A contract between a power producer and a client defining the price,
                    quantity, and duration of electricity sale.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card definition-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="definition-title">Equipment Rental Agreement (ERA)</p>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    A contract outlining rental duration, payment terms, and responsibilities
                    for equipment use between owner and renter.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Energy Storage as a Service</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
              Enercap electrostatic storage paired with AI-enabled power electronics sets
              a new standard for efficiency, reliability, and sustainability across
              energy-intensive applications.
            </p>
            <div class="feature-grid">
              <div class="card feature-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="card-title">Enercap Storage Technology</h4>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    Electrostatic storage offers long life, fast charging, non-degrading
                    performance, and safe, recyclable, and biodegradable materials.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card feature-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="card-title">Not a Chemical Battery</h4>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    Encapsulated capacitor cells are distinct from lithium-ion, LTO, or
                    hybrid battery systems.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card feature-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="card-title">Supercapacitor Control</h4>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    Algorithm-based control electronics manage active balancing in series
                    and parallel configurations, deliver a flat discharge curve, and
                    regulate self-discharge.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card feature-card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <h4 class="card-title">Beyond Supercaps</h4>
                  <p class="card-text">
                    Designed for energy-intensive applications across telecom, residential
                    backup, grid storage, EV charging, microgrids, and transportation.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Investment in Energy Efficiency Projects</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
              Financing solutions for efficient equipment upgrades that reduce energy
              wastage and deliver long-term savings.
            </p>
            <ul class="product-list" role="list">
              <li>Energy audit-driven retrofit programs</li>
              <li>Financing for high-efficiency equipment</li>
              <li>Performance-focused energy optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt" id="energy-storage">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Energy Storage Solutions</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          A lineup of energy storage platforms engineered for telecom, microgrid, grid,
          and EV applications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <a
            class="card-link"
            href="/products/energy-storage/ensirius/"
            aria-label="Telecom energy storage: Ensirius"
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Telecom</h3>
              <p class="card-text">
                Ensirius is the telecom go-to for long cycle life and degradation-free
                performance across BTS, data center, and fixed-line networks.
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <a
            class="card-link"
            href="/products/energy-storage/enbox/"
            aria-label="Microgrid energy storage: Enbox"
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Microgrid</h3>
              <p class="card-text">
                Enbox solutions provide reliable, stable, maintenance-free energy that can
                be deployed from kWh to MWh scale.
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <a
            class="card-link"
            href="/products/energy-storage/enpack/"
            aria-label="Grid energy storage: Enpack"
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">Grid</h3>
              <p class="card-text">
                Enpack platforms support grid services and renewable stability with a focus
                on lower LCOS and reduced environmental footprint.
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <a
            class="card-link"
            href="/products/energy-storage/batterix/"
            aria-label="EV energy storage: Batterix"
          >
            <div class="card-body">
              <h3 class="card-title">EV</h3>
              <p class="card-text">
                Batterix solutions are positioned for longer range, faster charging, wider
                operating temperature range, and extended life in EV applications.
              </p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">Residential</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">
          Scalable solar and storage solutions that empower households to transition
          to reliable, renewable energy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-grid">
        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Rent-to-Own Residential Solar</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
              The B-Smart project expands access to residential solar with tailored,
              convenient solutions designed for long-term energy independence.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
              We aim to develop and finance renewable energy infrastructure that makes
              clean power accessible to households across Pakistan.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="card-title">Residential Energy Storage</h3>
            <p class="card-text">
              Encap, Enwall, and Ensega systems deliver safe, longest-lasting, and
              environmentally sustainable storage that is easy to install, quick to
              commission, and degradation free.
            </p>
            <p class="card-text">
              Advanced materials science and power electronics provide predictable,
              reliable residential energy storage.
            </p>
            <div class="sub-card-grid">
              <a
                class="card sub-card-link"
                href="/products/energy-storage/encap/"
                aria-label="Encap residential storage"
              >
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="sub-card-title">Encap</p>
                </div>
              </a>
              <a
                class="card sub-card-link"
                href="/products/energy-storage/enwall/"
                aria-label="Enwall residential storage"
              >
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="sub-card-title">Enwall</p>
                </div>
              </a>
              <a
                class="card sub-card-link"
                href="/products/energy-storage/ensega/"
                aria-label="Ensega residential storage"
              >
                <div class="card-body">
                  <p class="sub-card-title">Ensega</p>
                </div>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Power Your Home or Business with Burj</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">
            Connect with our team to design a clean energy solution that fits your goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-900) 0%, var(--color-primary-700) 100%);
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
    padding-block: var(--space-20);
  }

  .page-hero-content {
    max-width: var(--container-3xl);
  }

  .page-eyebrow {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wide);
    font-size: var(--font-size-xs);
    color: var(--color-primary-200);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }

  .page-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    line-height: var(--line-height-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: var(--font-size-5xl);
    }
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    color: var(--color-primary-100);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .page-subtitle-group {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .product-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .product-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .product-list {
    margin: var(--space-4) 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
  }

  .product-list a {
    color: inherit;
  }

  .product-list a:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-700);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card-link {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .card-link:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sub-card-grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .sub-card-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .sub-card-link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .sub-card-link:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .sub-card-title {
    margin: 0;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--font-size-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .definition-grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .definition-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .definition-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wide);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .feature-grid {
    margin-top: var(--space-4);
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .feature-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }
  }

  .cta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cta {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
  }
</style>
